cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.DB

This paper deals with the investigation of cloud storage platforms from a forensic perspective, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves analyzing data remnants, which could be categorized under data management (cs.DC) and database systems (cs.DB). Additionally, the investigation of metadata changes on uploaded and downloaded files could be considered under the category of cybercrime (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
